text: @NCDCgov From 242 Covid19 cases today, 8 northern States are on the list and 5 southern States made the list.  100 cases from the South and 142 cases from the North. We should be concerned about the rate of spread in our Northern States. Few weeks ago, the list was dominated by SW states
